    "This bias leads to misclassifications when such features are needed to distinguish similar phases whose largest diffraction peaks overlap.",
    "Further complicating matters is the prevalence of measurement noise and diffuse background signal in experimental patterns, which often are not accounted for when training CNNs on simulated data 6.",
